title: Star Wars Symbolism Wrap-up

transcript_parts.text: hello everyone I wanted to wrap up the
Star Wars discussion that I started a
few weeks ago on what I had people
appeared to me as being somewhat
confused symbolism in the Star Wars
imagery of the force and the first thing
I have to say is I was amazed at
everybody how they participated in this
I mean I was really excited to read all
your comments I think after I think
after three days there were there was at
least 65 comments and so at first I
tried to keep up and to answer every one
but after a while I just I just couldn't
keep up but I mean I read all the
comments and it made me think a lot
about about the symbolism and I have to
say some of your ideas that some of the
ideas that people gave me were really
great the best idea I think that came
out of this was that we're dealing in
this in the Star Wars story with an
exceptional situation let's say a kind
of end of the world situation where
things are upside down and so I think
that makes a lot of sense and and a lot
of people pointed out that there's a
definite tension between between Darth
Vader the Emperor and the other aspects
of the Empire and some people pointed
out for example the scene where Vader
chokes the leaders you can see that
there's this it's kind of annoyance you
know people the the commanders of the of
the Death Star and the commanders of the
of the Empire they hate the this kind of
superstitious thing and at the same time
Vader he has he finds their their lack
of faith disturbing signs your lack of
faith disturbing as it says in the movie
so that's really what came out the most
and I really it helped me to help me to
understand what it could mean and the
fact that the in a way the Empire only

that it's really an end of the world
situation where extremes come together

so so that was interesting there's still
some issues that I have with why the

would be on the side of
this kind of rebellious group and

that I hadn't thought of that myself so
I really appreciate everybody's input
I'm going to be I'm trying with hoping

because I'm preparing for a talk that

I think it'll be thinking will be
